---
/* ScorecardExtras.astro
   Single-file component with multiple sections:
   - Two Ways to View Top Performers
   - Testimonial blue strip
   - Research & Press
   - About Us
   - Dark CTA split section
   - Footer / Newsletter
   Place images in /public/images/2023/ as noted below.
*/
---

<section class="two-ways">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2>Two Ways to View Top Performers</h2>

    <div class="two-ways-grid">
      <div class="col">
        <h4>Explore the Searchable Database</h4>
        <p>
          The online Scorecard's searchable database allows users to filter Top
          Performers by manufacturer, PQP test, module design, power class and
          more. Search results can be downloaded in CSV format for further
          analysis.
        </p>

        <div class="cta-card">
          <div class="cta-text">View the Top Performers →</div>
          <img
            src="/images/2023/cta-top-performers.gif"
            alt="Top performers preview"
            class="gif"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col">
        <h4>Download the Summary</h4>
        <p>
          Want to take the Scorecard offline? An executive summary of the 2023
          PV Module Reliability Scorecard is available for PDF download. The
          summary provides buyers with a quick reference to the list of top
          performing manufacturers along with key takeaways from PVEL’s PQP
          testing.
        </p>

        <div class="cta-card right-card">
          <div class="cta-text">Download the Summary →</div>
          <img
            src="/images/2023/cta-summary.jpg"
            alt="Summary cover"
            class="summary-img"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="testimonial">
  <div class="testimonial-inner">
    <blockquote>
      “Jinko has been using PVEL’s Product Qualification to demonstrate our
      commitment to quality and reliability since 2013, and we’re proud to be
      listed in the Scorecard for the ninth consecutive time. As our products
      evolve we are particularly thrilled to have our new n-type TOPCon modules
      featured prominently in this year’s Scorecard.”
    </blockquote>

    <div class="quote-meta">
      <div class="quote-author">
        <strong>Mr. Li Xiande</strong>
        <span
          >Chairman of the Board of Directors and Chief Executive Officer</span
        >
        <span>JinkoSolar Holding Co., Ltd.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="top-badge">
        <img
          src="/images/2023/top-performer-badge.webp"
          alt="Top performer badge"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="research-press">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2>Research and Press</h2>
    <div class="rp-grid">
      <div class="rp-left">
        <p>
          PVEL collaborates with the PV research community and media to share
          data that matters<br /> with the solar industry. Download the 2023 Scorecard
          Media Kit to learn<br /> more.
        </p>
        <p>
          For interview requests, contact <a href="mailto:pr@pvel.com"
            >pr@pvel.com</a
          >.
        </p>

        <a class="button" href="#">Learn More</a>
      </div>

      <div class="rp-right">
        <div class="logos">
          <img src="/images/2023/PV-Magazine-1.webp" alt="PV Magazine" />
          <img src="/images/2023/PV-Tech-1.webp" alt="PVTech" />
          <img
            src="/images/2023/Solar-Power-World-1.webp"
            alt="Solar Power World"
          />
          <img src="/images/2023/Solar-Builder-1.webp" alt="Solar Builder" />
          <img src="/images/2023/image-4.webp" alt="Exawatt" />
          <img src="/images/2023/image-5.webp" alt="Wood Mackenzie" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="about-us">
  <div class="wrap about-grid">
    <div class="about-left">
      <h2>About Us</h2>
      <p>
        PVEL, a member of the Kiwa Group, is the leading reliability and
        performance<br /> testing lab for downstream solar project developers, financiers,
        and asset<br /> owners around the world.
      </p>

      <p>
        PVEL and the Kiwa Group provide a suite of technical services for
        mitigating<br /> risk, optimizing financing and improving system performance
        throughout the<br /> project lifecycle.
      </p>

      <a class="button light" href="#">Learn More</a>
    </div>

    <div class="about-right">
      <img
        src="/images/2023/PVEL_EventCenter_Edited.jpg"
        alt="PVEL event center"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="dark-cta">
  <div class="wrap dark-grid">
    <div class="dark-left">
      <h3>
        Go beyond model types.<br />Procure PV modules with<br /> top-performing bills
        of<br /> materials.
      </h3>
      <p>Join PVEL’s downstream partner network.</p>
      <a class="button" href="#">Sign Up</a>
    </div>

    <div class="dark-right">
      <h3>Continue Exploring the<br /> 2023 Scorecard</h3>
      <a class="button outline" href="#">Next Page</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  :root {
    --wrap: 1200px;
    --muted-blue: #f3f7fe;
    --primary-blue: #163a78;
    --accent: #0a5bd3;
    --card-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(18, 34, 78, 0.08);
  }

  .wrap {
    max-width: var(--wrap);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }

  /* ---------------- Two Ways ---------------- */
  .two-ways {
    background: var(--muted-blue);
    padding: 64px 0 48px;
  }

  .two-ways h2 {
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 40.8px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    color: #0e0f13;
    line-height: 47.6px;
  }

  .two-ways-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .two-ways .col h4 {
    font-family: "Inter";
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .two-ways .col p {
    font-family: "Inter";
    color: #0e0f13;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .cta-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background: rgba(149, 171, 218, 0.85);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 28px;
    box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
    min-height: 80px;
    width: 600;
    margin-top: 70px;
    height: 115px;
  }

  .cta-text {
    font-size: 22px;
    color: #0e0f13;
    font-family: "Inter";
    font-weight: 400;
    width: 300px;
  }

  .right-card {
    background: rgba(149, 171, 218, 0.85);
    margin-top: 45px;
    height: 115px;
  }

  .summary-img {
    width: 110px;
    height: auto;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(18, 34, 78, 0.15);
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-left: 100px;
  }
  .gif {
    width: 300px;
    height: 140%;
    margin-right: -10px;
  }

  .top-badge {
    opacity: 1;
    /* width: px; */
  }

  /* ---------------- Testimonial (blue strip) ---------------- */
  .testimonial {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f3b78 0%, #244b86 55%, #1a386f 100%);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 64px 0;
  }

  .testimonial-inner {
    display: block;
    max-width: var(--wrap);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }

  .testimonial blockquote {
    font-size: 26px;
    line-height: 1.3;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 28px;
    max-width: 820px;
  }

  .quote-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .quote-author strong {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .quote-author span {
    display: block;
    opacity: 0.95;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .top-badge img {
    width: 120px;
    opacity: 0.95;
  }

  /* ---------------- Research & Press ---------------- */
  .research-press {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 48px 0;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .research-press h2 {
    margin-top: -20px;
    margin-bottom: 100px;
    font-size: 40.8px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    /* font-family: Chivo; */
  }

  .research-press h2::after {
    content: "";
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 100%; /* underline length */
    height: 1px;
    background: #e6e9f0; /* subtle light gray */
    margin-top: 18px; /* space between text & line */
  }
  .rp-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 360px;
    gap: 28px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .rp-left p {
    color: #0e0f13;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .logos {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 32px 40px;
    row-gap: 56px;
    align-items: center;
    justify-items: center;
    max-width: 420px;
    margin-left: -170px;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  .logos img {
    max-width: 120px;
    max-height: 48px;
    width: auto;
    height: auto;
    opacity: 1;
    filter: grayscale(100%);
  }

  .button {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 10px 18px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .button.light {
    background: #fff;
    color: var(--primary-blue);
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
  }

  /* ---------------- About ---------------- */
  .about-us {
    background: #30417f;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 64px 0;
  }
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 420px;
    gap: 28px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .about-left h2 {
    font-size: 36px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .about-left p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .about-right img {
    height: 280px;
    width: 480px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(6, 18, 48, 0.35);
    margin-top: 100px;
  }

  /* ---------------- Dark CTA area ---------------- */
  .dark-cta {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #21325a 0%, #2a3b6a 100%);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 60px 0;
  }
  .dark-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 30px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .dark-left h3,
  .dark-right h3 {
    font-size: 30px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    max-width: 520px;
  }
  .dark-left p {
    margin-top: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  }
  .button.outline {
    background: transparent;
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .button {
    color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
    background-color: rgb(10, 102, 194);
    width: 70px;
  }

  /* ---------------- Responsive ---------------- */
  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .two-ways-grid,
    .rp-grid,
    .about-grid,
    .footer-grid,
    .dark-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .cta-card {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .cta-card img {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: none;
    }
    .logos {
      justify-content: flex-start;
    }
    .testimonial blockquote {
      font-size: 20px;
    }
    .numbers-list {
      padding: 2rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .wrap {
      padding: 0 16px;
    }
    .two-ways h2 {
      font-size: 24px;
    }
    .testimonial blockquote {
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .about-left h2,
    .dark-left h3,
    .dark-right h3 {
      font-size: 20px;
    }
    .pvel-logo img {
      width: 140px;
    }
  }
</style>
